INSERT INTO document_comments (
            document_id, parent_comment_id, author_name, author_identifier,
            content, position_start, position_end, selected_text, comment_type,
            status, is_resolved, created_at, updated_at
        )
        VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)
        RETURNING id
